<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَنُحِبُّ رَبَّنَا، فَأَنْزَل اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَجَل الآْيَةَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَال الأَْزْهَرِيُّ:</span> مَحَبَّةُ الْعَبْدِ لِلَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِ طَاعَتُهُ لَهُمَا وَاتِّبَاعُهُ أَمْرَهُمَا <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَحْبُوسٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> حَبْسٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُحْتَسِبٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> حِسْبَةٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
